{"tid":1223451,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"個性獨立既女仔係點拍拖","createTime":"2019-06-14T17:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T15:14:44.000Z","uid":203710,"like":8,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e1c8227d47c178b881f29d58dabca1fe2c64457e","tid":1223451,"uid":203710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:00:27.000Z","msg":"男朋友比較懦弱，多愁善感，分人又好敏感，好驚其他人既目光，我好愛佢，但我真係唔識點鼓勵同安慰佢。<br />\n<br />\n佢覺得我生於好家庭，成日用黎比較自己有幾慘，我唔介意佢家庭背景，想同佢一齊變好，自問係一個努力既人，見佢搵分part time 都驚，唔敢面對社會，我選擇左逼佢，至少自己可以三餐食好d...從來冇要求佢買咩比我，但佢成日自暴自棄，見佢咁樣我真係好心痛，即使佢對我控制慾好強（男仔係唔可以follow 我ig的），我都對佢不離不棄，但我真係好攰...我好現實，好努力讀書同搵錢，佢為左我都好努力，但永遠都比我想像中唔夠努力，其實男仔就係永遠都唔肯長大...面對現實？<br />\n<br />\n利申我19佢20"},{"pid":"45cddaa604aad34aa2b1d84b139fb4ca9c8a67be","tid":1223451,"uid":63311,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:01:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>反送中, 撤回修例.<br />\n<br />\n星期日出去遊行.<br />\n<br />\n星期一出去集會<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"937a48bbf39d38d71559fc68926003378bd11536","tid":1223451,"uid":203710,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"quote":{"pid":"45cddaa604aad34aa2b1d84b139fb4ca9c8a67be","tid":1223451,"uid":63311,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:01:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>反送中, 撤回修例.<br />\n<br />\n星期日出去遊行.<br />\n<br />\n星期一出去集會<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:01:53.000Z","msg":"如果我男朋友都肯出去就好..."},{"pid":"c512d1cc5bccb7a586f4fe801aeda5ccb549c372","tid":1223451,"uid":63311,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"937a48bbf39d38d71559fc68926003378bd11536","tid":1223451,"uid":203710,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"quote":{"pid":"45cddaa604aad34aa2b1d84b139fb4ca9c8a67be","tid":1223451,"uid":63311,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:01:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\